message: /* top */ The SI symbol for kilometres is km, not kms

Kullada is basically a place 8 Km. away from the City Bhanjanagar. Previously Bhanjanagar was known as many names such as Ghumsur, Rossel Konda. After the name of Kabi Samrat Upendra Bhanja the city was named Bhanjanagar. Berhampur or Brahmapur is 80 Kms or so away from Kullada. Hence, Bhanjanagar will be more accurate to describe the birth place of Kabi Samrat Upendra Bhanja.
